      "title": "Fogging by CMC to dispel mosquitoes",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Colombo Municipal Council (CMC) has taken steps to start fogging to prevent the spread of dengue virus in the Colombo municipality areas, including Vidyala Mawatha in District 2, MOH office in Colombo 13, as a precautionary measure to control the mosquitoes. Pix by Nimalsiri Edirisinghe"
